{"tid":2355654,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【親自指揮 親自部署】河北省 疫情持續擴大","createTime":"2021-01-06T08:42:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T00:36:20.000Z","uid":293677,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"6567ccba3fbaac756757bd112bf8b3ac37a92f20","tid":2355654,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T08:42:26.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><ins>疫情從村擴至全區！ 河北石家莊藁城區列中國唯一「高風險地區」</ins></span><br />\n<br />\n2021/01/06 15:46<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國武漢肺炎（新型冠狀病毒病，COVID-19）疫情再起，河北省昨（5）日新增20例本土病例、43例本地無症狀感染者，其中主要集中在石家莊市，河北省衛健委今日宣布，將石家莊市藁城區全域調整為「高風險地區」，成為中國現在唯一的高風險地區。<br />\n<br />\n綜合中媒報導，河北省疫情持續擴大，5日石家莊市出現19例本土病例、41例無症狀感染者，河北省衛健委中午宣布，將石家莊市藁城區列為「高風險地區」。也是中國自疫情初期以來，罕見的再將整個縣級行政區列入高風險。<br />\n<br />\n藁城區的增村鎮小果莊村由於出現群聚感染，5日全村已被列為「高風險地區」，隨著疫情蔓延，河北省衛健委今（6）日宣布將高風險範圍從村擴至全區域。河北省邢台市南宮市天地名城小區、邢台市南宮市天一和院小區、邢台市南宮市鳳崗街道辦事處則為中風險地區，其他地區維持低風險。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">河北省衛健委表示，根據中國當局疫情應對措施要求，河北省立即進入戰時狀態</span></span>，省級疫情工作小組也已向石家莊市、邢台市派出團隊指導疫情處置工作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3402915\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3402915&d=dNeHxx%2FttK3%2FgpwSwFVImS%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=8a88cdaf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3402915&h=0e9d96dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3402915</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"limegreen\"><span class=\"x-large\">註：北京天津係俾河北省包圍住架</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"642299e164713b3663a220841e9d94b99f55e631","tid":2355654,"uid":276273,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T08:48:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b22Ww2G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb22Ww2G.jpg&h=c1b57a45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n背後既嘢，有幾多人睇得明呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73cee9b888795cbff6b91fa88356bb75a59dcb26","tid":2355654,"uid":279981,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T08:54:21.000Z","msg":"鎖你老味 隨時開戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18dc7fa13a269514f4e7bf51359f0fd0e062d183","tid":2355654,"uid":253016,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T08:55:31.000Z","msg":"我唯一關心既事就係支那豬幾時死清光?"},{"pid":"30e1fda567feeb0d1d1eb23a32054ef158e067d9","tid":2355654,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18dc7fa13a269514f4e7bf51359f0fd0e062d183","tid":2355654,"uid":253016,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T08:55:31.000Z","msg":"我唯一關心既事就係支那豬幾時死清光?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T08:56:37.000Z","msg":"14億加小強生命力"},{"pid":"ad092a9439be2e9fcb3c2c1708a3c0841e1532b2","tid":2355654,"uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T08:57:10.000Z","msg":"擴散出去啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9423f76a30c103deacc3e98716a20281dfa1389a","tid":2355654,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T08:57:48.000Z","msg":"死7億仲有7億，好小事"},{"pid":"5fc941b909e503e316ce7ec1e9398658c77624e3","tid":2355654,"uid":321002,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T19:29:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21c1018a2a151ad61a0ad770d388d2214ba36dc4","tid":2355654,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T20:06:25.000Z","msg":"Fake news!<br />\n支那一直零確診<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3f5551961d0b78e9e5e31a7f87da87e134328a5","tid":2355654,"uid":51271,"like"